{"tid":1020464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《紅日》被改成《2月14顛沛流離　李克勤：真係想唱一唱...","createTime":"2019-02-13T15:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T04:44:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2a137fa6e93a9c4c6215e9d82b11eb85693cb9","tid":1020464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190213/s00009/096e91ddaa7fdab9e51f8c776d557313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190213%2Fs00009%2F096e91ddaa7fdab9e51f8c776d557313.jpg&h=5a19dd8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天是情人節，是情侶們放閃曬恩愛日子，有網民將李克勤經典歌《紅日》改詞，將這首勵志歌變成「單身歌曲」《2月14顛沛流離》，不少網民更留言表示希望克勤能唱這個改詞版本。<br />\n<br />\n身在內地工作的克勤，今晚亦在社交網上載網民改編的歌詞，他說：「我人在賓陽工作 知道大家咁俾（畀）面 本來真係想唱一唱 反正我也不是什麼斯文人 但又驚啲仔睇到聽到 你知呢啲嘢小朋友學得最快...😅😅😅 祝大家情人節快樂 單身的就盡快脫單 謝謝大家。」"},{"pid":"115fba061dfb930e2ae17caab8199c07c854944c","tid":1020464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190213/1550069570331/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190213%2F1550069570331%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=219b9b02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190213%2F1550069570331%2F&h=0f6d5266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190213/1550069570331/</a>"},{"pid":"056792aff8d6019c2d51bb652e16432fa456ebe3","tid":1020464,"uid":29080,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃！"},{"pid":"86f70356c8f25be58b4b4a831226d493e8c25234","tid":1020464,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"唱兩句都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5333137c0cfa32355948e95